Package: sba
Title: SBA (Small Business Administration) Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the SBA open data portal (data.sba.gov).
    Provides discovery and access to SBA datasets including loan programs (7a, 504,
    PPP, EIDL), disaster loans, size standards, HUBZone designations, and more.
    Built on the CKAN v3 Action API.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    dplyr,
    tibble
